{"id": "1249351866890846258", "channel_id": "1247963491512487936", "type": 0, "author_id": "781400757924397086", "author_name": "lin7434", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過回到這反應的主題\n忘卻沒用那些限定角  也沒到不能玩的程度\n上次加強那些常駐角  可玩性是有上升的\n就看玩家有沒有想要研究", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T13:18:16.902000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247963491512487936", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫出来说话", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1249355201110999122", "channel_id": "1247963491512487936", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "現版本沒超限還是每個界域都有滿分大佬\n怎麼會有抽不到超限玩不了的問題", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T13:31:31.842000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247963491512487936", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫出来说话", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
