{"id": "1249357809242603540", "channel_id": "1247963491512487936", "type": 0, "author_id": "781400757924397086", "author_name": "lin7434", "author_bot": false, "content": "阿紅連給個易傷都沒有 真的好卑微", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T13:41:53.669000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247963491512487936", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫出来说话", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1249357972992163901", "channel_id": "1247963491512487936", "type": 0, "author_id": "781400757924397086", "author_name": "lin7434", "author_bot": false, "content": "技能發動 就阿紅最多毛還爛\n看上去 就算不限50%血 也不是多麼厲害的技能", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T13:42:32.710000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247963491512487936", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫出来说话", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1249360849806688296", "channel_id": "1247963491512487936", "type": 19, "author_id": "781400757924397086", "author_name": "lin7434", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果角色都是這種加強 就真的很不明顯\n就沒有直接加到暴強的問題\n\n阿紅機制都走單回合的流派\n我還是覺得這角色很難用  甚麼都要屈就她\n然後才能出現效果 簡單來說就是難用", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T13:53:58.596000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["232848201500065792"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1249357290205872259", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247963491512487936", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫出来说话", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
